  "id": "019d286a-f2d7-7750-81b8-29e8e715e3e4",
  "content": "# M3.3: Embedding & Chunking Strategy Implementation Plan\n\n> **Status:** Shipped (v0.3.0)\n\n**Goal:** Build a trait-based chunking framework with five format strategies, a kernel orchestrator pipeline, and revised ingestion flow — completing D65-D69.\n\n**Architecture:** `ChunkingPipeline` orchestrates format routing via `FormatRegistry`, delegating to `ChunkingStrategy` implementations (FallbackChunker, MarkdownChunker, ConfigChunker, PdfChunker, AstChunker). The `IngestionAdapter` trait is revised per D69 to return raw `SourceFile`s instead of `KnowledgeEntry`s. The pipeline handles universal concerns: merge small → enforce budget → split oversized → overlap context.\n\n**Tech Stack:** Rust (edition 2024), tree-sitter (AST), pdf-extract (PDF text), existing corvia-kernel token_estimator + chunking_strategy types.\n\n---\n",
